The following script is provided as practical example. It configures the function generator in
arbitrary waveform signal data mode.
characterization test for 11 voltage levels and reports the corresponding current measurements.

Edit networks.xml adding the NETCONF access parameters for your device.

Usage:

python3 test.py --config=networks.xml


# 10 second 1 KHz - 2 KHz linear chirp is played on the default ALSA device with aplay
